cs.HC, cs.LG, cs.IR, cs.DB, cs.CV 

The paper discusses the use of visual analytics to aid users in generating models for a diverse set of data and modeling tasks. This involves the use of automated machine learning (autoML) systems, which are typically used in the fields of human-computer interaction (cs.HC), machine learning (cs.LG), information retrieval (cs.IR), databases (cs.DB), and computer vision (cs.CV). Therefore, these are the most likely arXiv CS sub-categories for this paper.
